\\docs\\sops\\CHROME-DEVTOOLS-AI-MECHANISM.md:\n  Line 361: | \"The .ailog schema is from Chrome\" | **Inference, not confirmed** |\n\n  Line 423: ## The .ailog Schema (Original)\n\n  Line 425: Chrome DevTools AI originally used the `.ailog` schema:\n\n\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\find_agentson_minimax.py:\n  Line 19:        OR sm.data LIKE '%.ailog%'\n\n\n(Some paths were inaccessible and skipped)",
