      "output": "commit d5d0e85bf28153899e5db482b9f8a69375e7e27e\nAuthor: andiekobbie <andiekobbietks@outlook.com>\nDate:   Sun Jul 5 02:19:43 2026 +0100\n\n    AgentSON v0.1 — clean history (no PII)\n    \n    Vendor-neutral JSON format for AI agent sessions.\n    Readers: opencode, minimax, antigravity, libre.\n    Exporters: Unsloth (ShareGPT), Olive.\n    Importers: ChatGPT.\n    CLI: export, import, list, search, finetune, render, push, pull.\n    PWA: drag-and-drop viewer, offline support.\n    Spec: JSON Schema v1.\n    Landing page included.\n\n .gitignore                                         |  35 +\n MANIFEST.in                                        |  12 +\n PERSONAS-AND-USER-STORIES.md                       | 301 +++++++++\n PRD.md                                             | 718 +++++++++++++++++++++\n README.md                                          | 300 +++++++++\n SOPs/SOP-001-Reading-FreeStyle-Libre-2-Sensor.md   | 108 ++++\n SOPs/SOP-002-Converting-Libre-Data-to-AgentSON.md  |  93 +++\n SOPs/SOP-003-Viewing-Glucose-Data-in-Browser.md    | 105 +++\n SOPs/SOP-004-Exporting-AI-Sessions.md              |  88 +++\n SOPs/SOP-005-Searching-AI-Sessions.md              |  82 +++\n SOPs/SOP-006-Sharing-Data-with-Doctors.md          |  91 +++\n SOPs/SOP-007-Setting-Up-Nightscout-Server.md       | 134 ++++\n SOPs/SOP-008-WhatsApp-Bot-Setup.md                 | 135 ++++\n SOPs/SOP-009-TV-Dashboard-Setup.md                 | 138 ++++\n SOPs/SOP-010-Setting-Up-MedGemma-HAI-DEF.md        |  94 +++\n ...SOP-011-Fine-tuning-MedGemma-on-Glucose-Data.md | 127 ++++\n ...SOP-012-Setting-Up-Juggluco-on-Mothers-Phone.md | 115 ++++\n SOPs/SOP-013-NHS-FHIR-Integration.md               | 175 +++++\n SOPs/SOP-014-West-Africa-Voice-Alerts.md           | 204 ++++++\n cli/main.py                                        | 572 ++++++++++++++++\n cli/supabase_client.py                             | 207 ++++++\n docs/index.html                                    | 428 +++++++