      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\agentsong\\docs\\index.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: <!DOCTYPE html>\n2: <html lang=\"en\">\n3: <head>\n4:     <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n5:     <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n6:     <title>AgentSON — Agent + JSON</title>\n7:     <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n8:     <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n9:     <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n10:     <style>\n11:         :root {\n12:             --bg: #0a0a08;\n13:             --surface: #141410;\n14:             --border: #2a2a1e;\n15:             --text: #e8e0c8;\n16:             --text-muted: #9a9070;\n17:             --accent: #ffb000;\n18:             --success: #a0d060;\n19:             --warning: #ffb000;\n20:             --error: #e05040;\n21:         }\n22: \n23:         * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n24: \n25:         body {\n26:             font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n27:             background: var(--bg);\n28:             color: var(--text);\n29:             line-height: 1.6;\n30:         }\n31: \n32:         code, pre, .mono {\n33:             font-family: 'Space Mono', 'Consolas', 'Monaco', monospace;\n34:         }\n35: \n36:         .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }\n37: \n38:         header {\n39:             text-align: center;\n40:             padding: 60px 20px;\n41:             border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n42:         }\n43: \n44:         h1 {\n45:             font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n46:             font-size: 48px;\n47:             margin-bottom: 10px;\n48:         }\n49:         h1 span { color: var(--accent); }\n50: \n51:         .tagline {\n52:             font-size: 20px;\n53:             color: var(--text-muted);\n54:             margin-bottom: 30px;\n55:         }\n56: \n57:         .badge {\n58:             display: inline-block;\n59:             padding: 8px 16px;\n60:             background: var(--accent);\n61:             color: #0a0a08;\n62:             border-radius: 20px;\n63:             font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n64:             font-weight: 600;\n65:             margin: 5px;\n66:             font-size: 0.85rem;\n67:         }\n68: \n69:         section { padding: 60px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }\n70: \n71:         h2 {\n72:             font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n73:             font-size: 32px;\n74:             margin-bottom: 20px;\n75:             color: var(--accent);\n76:         }\n77:         h3 { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 15px; }\n78: \n79:         .grid {\n80:             display: grid;\n81:             grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n82:             gap: 20px;\n83:             margin-top: 30px;\n84:         }\n85: \n86:         .card {\n87:             background: var(--surface);\n88:             border: 1px solid var(--border);\n89:             border-radius: 8px;\n90:             padding: 24px;\n91:         }\n92: \n93:         .card h3 { color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; }\n94:         .card p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px; }\n95: \n96:         .status {\n97:             display: inline-block;\n98:             padding: 4px 8px;\n99:             border-radius: 4px;\n100:             font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n101:             font-size: 12px;\n102:             font-weight: 600;\n103:         }\n104: \n105:         .status-done { background: var(--success); color: #0a0a08; }\n106:         .status-progress { background: var(--warning); color: #0a0a08; }\n107:         .status-planned { background: var(--text-muted); color: #0a0a08; }\n108: \n109:         pre {\n110:             background: var(--bg);\n111:             padding: 16px;\n112:             border-radius: 8px;\n113:             overflow-x: auto;\n114:             margin: 20px 0;\n115:             border: 1px solid var(--border);\n116:         }\n117: \n118:         code {\n119:             font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n120:             font-size: 14px;\n121:         }\n122: \n123:         .btn {\n124:             display: inline-block;\n125:             padding: 12px 24px;\n126:             background: var(--accent);\n127:             color: #0a0a08;\n128:             text-decoration: none;\n129:             border-radius: 6px;\n130:             font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n131:             font-weight: 600;\n132:             margin: 10px 5px;\n133:         }\n134: \n135:         .btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; }\n136: \n137:         .btn-outline {\n138:             background: transparent;\n139:             border: 1px solid var(--accent);\n140:             color: var(--accent);\n141:         }\n142: \n143:         .stats {\n144:             display: flex;\n145:             justify-content: center;\n146:             gap: 40px;\n147:             margin-top: 30px;\n148:         }\n149: \n150:         .stat { text-align: center; }\n151:         .stat-value {\n152:             font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n153:             font-size: 36px;\n154:             font-weight: 700;\n155:             color: var(--accent);\n156:         }\n157:         .stat-label { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); }\n158: \n159:         .sop-grid {\n160:             display: grid;\n161:             grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n162:             gap: 12px;\n163:             margin-top: 20px;\n164:         }\n165: \n166:         .sop-item {\n167:             background: var(--surface);\n168:             border: 1px solid var(--border);\n169:             border-radius: 6px;\n170:             padding: 12px 16px;\n171:             display: flex;\n172:             gap: 12px;\n173:             align-items: center;\n174:         }\n175: \n176:         .sop-num {\n177:             font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n178:             font-size: 12px;\n179:             color: var(--accent);\n180:             font-weight: 700;\n181:             min-width: 60px;\n182:         }\n183: \n184:         .sop-title { font-size: 14px; }\n185: \n186:         footer {\n187:             text-align: center;\n188:             padding: 40px 20px;\n189:             color: var(--text-muted);\n190:             font-size: 14px;\n191:         }\n192: \n193:         footer a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }\n194: \n195:         @media (max-width: 768px) {\n196:             h1 { font-size: 32px; }\n197:             .stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }\n198:             .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n199:         }\n200:     </style>\n201: </head>\n202: <body>\n203:     <header>\n204:         <h1><span>Agent</span>SON</h1>\n205:         <p class=\"tagline\">Agent + JSON — Yet Another JSON, but metadata-rich and built for the agentic era.</p>\n206:         <div>\n207:             <span class=\"badge\">Open Source</span>\n208:             <span class=\"badge\">Free Forever</span>\n209:             <span class=\"badge\">NHS Ready</span>\n210:         </div>\n211:         <div style=\"margin-top: 30px;\">\n212:             <a href=\"https://github.com/andiekobbietks/AgentSON\" class=\"btn\">GitHub</a>\n213:             <a href=\"viewer/\" class=\"btn btn-outline\">Launch Viewer</a>\n214:             <a href=\"sops/\" class=\"btn btn-outline\">SOPs</a>\n215:         </div>\n216:     </header>\n217: \n218:     <section>\n219:         <h2>The Problem</h2>\n220:         <p>Every AI coding agent stores session data in its own proprietary SQLite database. There is no standard format, no export API, and no way to move context between tools.</p>\n221:         <div class=\"grid\">\n222:             <div class=\"card\">\n223:                 <h3>opencode</h3>\n224:                 <p>21 tables, custom schema, no export API</p>\n225:             </div>\n226:             <div class=\"card\">\n227:                 <h3>MiniMax</h3>\n228:                 <p>20 tables, different schema, no portability</p>\n229:             </div>\n230:             <div class=\"card\">\n231:                 <h3>Antigravity IDE</h3>\n232:                 <p>7 tables, protobuf blobs, no standardization</p>\n233:             </div>\n234:         </div>\n235:     </section>\n236: \n237:     <section>\n238:         <h2>The Solution</h2>\n239:         <p>AgentSON provides a vendor-neutral format for agent session capture.</p>\n240:         <div class=\"grid\">\n241:             <div class=\"card\">\n242:                 <h3>Specification</h3>\n243:                 <p>JSON Schema for agent session data</p>\n244:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n245:             </div>\n246:             <div class=\"card\">\n247:                 <h3>Readers</h3>\n248:                 <p>SQLite parsers for opencode, MiniMax, Antigravity</p>\n249:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n250:             </div>\n251:             <div class=\"card\">\n252:                 <h3>CLI</h3>\n253:                 <p>Export, search, render, push/pull</p>\n254:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n255:             </div>\n256:             <div class=\"card\">\n257:                 <h3>Web Viewer</h3>\n258:                 <p>Drag & drop visualization</p>\n259:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n260:             </div>\n261:             <div class=\"card\">\n262:                 <h3>Glucose Reader</h3>\n263:                 <p>FreeStyle Libre 2 CSV → AgentSON</p>\n264:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n265:             </div>\n266:             <div class=\"card\">\n267:                 <h3>SOPs</h3>\n268:                 <p>14 Standard Operating Procedures</p>\n269:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n270:             </div>\n271:         </div>\n272:     </section>\n273: \n274:     <section>\n275:         <h2>Quick Start</h2>\n276:         <pre><code># List sessions\n277: python cli/main.py list --tool opencode\n278: \n279: # Export a session\n280: python cli/main.py export --tool opencode --session ses_xxx\n281: \n282: # Export glucose data\n283: python cli/main.py export --tool libre --input libre_data.csv\n284: \n285: # Push to Supabase\n286: python cli/main.py push session.AgentSON\n287: \n288: # Pull from Supabase\n289: python cli/main.py pull --search \"nightscout\"</code></pre>\n290:     </section>\n291: \n292:     <section>\n293:         <h2>Supported Tools</h2>\n294:         <div class=\"grid\">\n295:             <div class=\"card\">\n296:                 <h3>opencode</h3>\n297:                 <p>Working</p>\n298:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n299:             </div>\n300:             <div class=\"card\">\n301:                 <h3>MiniMax</h3>\n302:                 <p>Working</p>\n303:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n304:             </div>\n305:             <div class=\"card\">\n306:                 <h3>Antigravity IDE</h3>\n307:                 <p>Working</p>\n308:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n309:             </div>\n310:             <div class=\"card\">\n311:                 <h3>FreeStyle Libre 2</h3>\n312:                 <p>Working</p>\n313:                 <span class=\"status status-done\">Done</span>\n314:             </div>\n315:             <div class=\"card\">\n316:                 <h3>Cursor</h3>\n317:                 <p>Planned</p>\n318:                 <span class=\"status status-planned\">Planned</span>\n319:             </div>\n320:             <div class=\"card\">\n321:                 <h3>Claude Code</h3>\n322:                 <p>Planned</p>\n323:                 <span class=\"status status-planned\">Planned</span>\n324:             </div>\n325:         </div>\n326:     </section>\n327: \n328:     <section>\n329:         <h2>Diabetes Monitoring</h2>\n330:         <p>AgentSON powers real-time glucose monitoring for carers and clinicians.</p>\n331:         <div class=\"stats\">\n332:             <div class=\"stat\">\n333:                 <div class=\"stat-value\">571</div>\n334:                 <div class=\"stat-label\">Glucose Readings</div>\n335:             </div>\n336:             <div class=\"stat\">\n337:                 <div class=\"stat-value\">9.33</div>\n338:                 <div class=\"stat-label\">Avg mmol/L</div>\n339:             </div>\n340:             <div class=\"stat\">\n341:                 <div class=\"stat-value\">60.6%</div>\n342:                 <div class=\"stat-label\">Time in Range</div>\n343:             </div>\n344:             <div class=\"stat\">\n345:                 <div class=\"stat-value\">14</div>\n346:                 <div class=\"stat-label\">SOPs Written</div>\n347:             </div>\n348:         </div>\n349:     </section>\n350: \n351:     <section>\n352:         <h2>SOPs (Standard Operating Procedures)</h2>\n353:         <div class=\"sop-grid\">\n354:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-001</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Reading FreeStyle Libre 2 Sensor</span></div>\n355:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-002</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Converting Libre Data to AgentSON</span></div>\n356:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-003</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Viewing Glucose Data in Browser</span></div>\n357:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-004</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Exporting AI Sessions</span></div>\n358:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-005</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Searching AI Sessions</span></div>\n359:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-006</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Sharing Data with Doctors</span></div>\n360:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-007</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Setting Up Nightscout Server</span></div>\n361:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-008</span><span class=\"sop-title\">WhatsApp Bot Setup</span></div>\n362:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-009</span><span class=\"sop-title\">TV Dashboard Setup</span></div>\n363:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-010</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Setting Up MedGemma/HAI-DEF</span></div>\n364:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-011</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Fine-tuning MedGemma on Glucose Data</span></div>\n365:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-012</span><span class=\"sop-title\">Setting Up Juggluco on Mother's Phone</span></div>\n366:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-013</span><span class=\"sop-title\">NHS FHIR Integration</span></div>\n367:             <div class=\"sop-item\"><span class=\"sop-num\">SOP-014</span><span class=\"sop-title\">West Africa Voice Alerts</span></div>\n368:         </div>\n369:     </section>\n370: \n371:     <section>\n372:         <h2>The Stack</h2>\n373:         <pre><code>DATA COLLECTION:\n374: ├── Juggluco (mother's phone)\n375: ├── FreeStyle Libre 2 (sensor)\n376: └── Manual entry (CHWs in West Africa)\n377: \n378: DATA STORAGE:\n379: ├── Nightscout (self-hosted)\n380: ├── AgentSON (.AgentSON files)\n381: └── Supabase (optional cloud)\n382: \n383: AI/ML:\n384: ├── MedGemma (Google HAI-DEF)\n385: ├── Fine-tuned glucose model\n386: └── MedASR (speech-to-text)\n387: \n388: ALERTS:\n389: ├── WhatsApp (whatsapp-web.js)\n390: ├── SMS (Africa's Talking)\n391: ├── Voice (Coqui TTS)\n392: └── TV Dashboard\n393: \n394: CLINICAL:\n395: ├── NHS FHIR (intu)\n396: ├── EMIS/SystmOne (when available)\n397: └── GP reports (HTML/PDF)\n398: \n399: DEVELOPER TOOLS:\n400: ├── Backstage (documentation portal)\n401: ├── AgentSON (session portability)\n402: └── GitHub (version control)</code></pre>\n403:     </section>\n404: \n405:     <section>\n406:         <h2>Cost</h2>\n407:         <div class=\"grid\">\n408:             <div class=\"card\">\n409:                 <h3>Build Cost</h3>\n410:                 <p style=\"font-size: 36px; color: var(--success);\">£0</p>\n411:                 <p>All open source, free tools</p>\n412:             </div>\n413:             <div class=\"card\">\n414:                 <h3>Running Cost</h3>\n415:                 <p style=\"font-size: 36px; color: var(--success);\">£2-5/month</p>\n416:                 <p>Electricity only</p>\n417:             </div>\n418:             <div class=\"card\">\n419:                 <h3>NHS Equivalent</h3>\n420:                 <p style=\"font-size: 36px; color: var(--error);\">£50-200/month</p>\n421:                 <p>Proprietary systems</p>\n422:             </div>\n423:         </div>\n424:     </section>\n425: \n426:     <section>\n427:         <h2>Get Started</h2>\n428:         <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n429:             <a href=\"https://github.com/andiekobbietks/AgentSON\" class=\"btn\">View on GitHub</a>\n430:             <a href=\"viewer/\" class=\"btn btn-outline\">Launch Web Viewer</a>\n431:             <a href=\"sops/\" class=\"btn btn-outline\">Read SOPs</a>\n432:         </div>\n433:     </section>\n434: \n435:     <footer>\n436:         <p>AgentSON — Agent + JSON</p>\n437:         <p>Built with ❤️ for carers, clinicians, and communities.</p>\n438:         <p>© 2026 Andrea Enning (AndieKobbieTech)</p>\n439:     </footer>\n440: </body>\n441: </html>\n\n(End of file - total 441 lines)\n</content>",
